results.sql: SELECT TRIM(Account.name) AS `AccountName`, Account.id AS `AccountID`, Account.status AS `AccountStatus`, Contractor.membershipdate AS `ContractorMembershipDate`, Account.city AS `AccountCity`, Account.countrysubdivision AS `AccountCountrySubdivision`, Account.country AS `AccountCountry` FROM contractor_info AS Contractor JOIN accounts AS Account ON Contractor.id = Account.id AND Account.type = 'Contractor' WHERE ((Account.status IN ('Active','Pending'))) ORDER BY AccountName
